{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 8296905}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Por Resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xB0; 1.333, de 18 de julio de 1996, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a de Pesca, del Ministerio de Econom&#xED;a, Fomento y Reconstrucci&#xF3;n; modif&#xED;case el numeral 2 de la Resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xB0; 480, de 1983, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, que autoriz&#xF3; a PESQUERA IQUIQUE S.A., hoy Pesquera Iquique Guanaye S.A., para realizar actividades pesqueras extractivas con las naves &quot;Vinga&quot; y &quot;Timor&quot; en el sentido de se&#xF1;alar sus actuales caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas.</div><div class=\"p\"> Nombre&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Cullinto&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Timor</div><div class=\"p\"> Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2365&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2366</div><div class=\"p\"> Eslora de arqueo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  44,16 m&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  44,16 m.</div><div class=\"p\"> Manga&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  9,50 m&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 9,50 m.</div><div class=\"p\"> Puntal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7,30 m&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7,30 m.</div><div class=\"p\"> T.R.G.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 566,39&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 566,39</div><div class=\"p\"> T.R.N.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 155,30&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 155,30</div><div class=\"p\"> Cap. de Bodega&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 607,00 m3&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  607,00 m3</div><div class=\"p\"> Arte de Pesca&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Cerco&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Cerco</div><br></div>", "i": 8296906}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Valpara&#xED;so, 18 de julio de 1996.- Patric